<DOCUMENT source-infobase-name="Admin" content-collection-id="NYCadmin" source-infobase-title="New York City Administrative Code" base-output-dir="D:\process\NFOProcess\codes\ny\newyorkcity\NYCadmin\output\QYOUGRVBABWOEQAB\" default-split-level="Chapter" makefile-filename="D:\process\NFOProcess\codes\ny\newyorkcity\NYCadmin\output\QYOUGRVBABWOEQAB\NYCadmin.mak" css-stylesheet-href="#!-- #ID=NYCadmin_css_id --#" xml-output-dir="D:\process\NFOProcess\codes\ny\newyorkcity\NYCadmin\output\QYOUGRVBABWOEQAB\XML\" css-stylesheet-name="NYCadmin_css" makefile-document-depth="2">
	<LEVEL style-name="Chapter" style-name-escaped="Chapter" style-id="0-0-0-685" level-depth="2" toc-section="false">
		<RECORD id="0-0-0-114071" number="61223" version="235">
			<HEADING>Chapter 27: Mitchell-Lama Development Reporting Requirements</HEADING>
			<PARA>
				<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-19417" name="T26C027"/>Chapter 27: Mitchell-Lama Development Reporting Requirements</PARA>
		</RECORD>
		<LEVEL style-name="Subchapter" style-name-escaped="Subchapter" style-id="0-0-0-688" level-depth="3" toc-section="false">
			<LEVEL style-name="Appendix" style-name-escaped="Appendix" style-id="0-0-0-691" level-depth="4" toc-section="false">
				<LEVEL style-name="Part" style-name-escaped="Part" style-id="0-0-0-694" level-depth="5" toc-section="false">
					<LEVEL style-name="Article" style-name-escaped="Article" style-id="0-0-0-697" level-depth="6" toc-section="false">
						<LEVEL style-name="Subarticle" style-name-escaped="Subarticle" style-id="0-0-0-700" level-depth="7" toc-section="false">
							<LEVEL style-name="Subarticle - Part" style-name-escaped="Subarticle---Part" style-id="0-0-0-29474" level-depth="8" toc-section="false">
								<LEVEL style-name="Section" style-name-escaped="Section" style-id="0-0-0-703" level-depth="9" toc-section="true">
									<RECORD id="0-0-0-114072" number="61224" version="235">
										<HEADING>§ 26-2701 Definitions.</HEADING>
										<PARA>
											<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-19419" name="26-2701"/>§ 26-2701 Definitions.</PARA>
									</RECORD>
									<LEVEL style-name="Normal Level" style-name-escaped="Normal-Level" style-id="0-0-0-0" level-depth="0" toc-section="false">
										<RECORD id="0-0-0-114089" number="61225" version="235">
											<PARA>As used in this chapter, the following terms have the following meanings: <HIGHLIGHTER style="ALP" style-name-escaped="ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-25">[ALP S-044]</HIGHLIGHTER>
											</PARA>
										</RECORD>
										<RECORD id="0-0-0-114088" number="61226" version="1765">
											<PARA>
												<TAB tab-count="1"/>
												<CHARFORMAT bold="1" italic="0" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Department.</CHARFORMAT> The term &quot;department&quot; means the department of housing preservation and development. <HIGHLIGHTER style="ALP" style-name-escaped="ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-25">[ALP S-044]</HIGHLIGHTER>
											</PARA>
										</RECORD>
										<RECORD id="0-0-0-114087" number="61227" version="1765">
											<PARA>
												<TAB tab-count="1"/>
												<CHARFORMAT bold="1" italic="0" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Mitchell-Lama development.</CHARFORMAT> The term &quot;Mitchell-Lama development&quot; means a housing development organized pursuant to article two of the private housing finance law and supervised by the department. <HIGHLIGHTER style="ALP" style-name-escaped="ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-25">[ALP S-044]</HIGHLIGHTER>
											</PARA>
										</RECORD>
										<RECORD id="0-0-0-114086" number="61228" version="1765">
											<PARA>
												<TAB tab-count="1"/>
												<CHARFORMAT bold="1" italic="0" underline="0" strike-out="0" hidden="0">Waiting list.</CHARFORMAT> The term &quot;waiting list&quot; means a list of applicants from which the managing agent of a Mitchell-Lama development is required to process potential tenants or shareholders as applicable for subsequent occupancies of such development. <HIGHLIGHTER style="ALP" style-name-escaped="ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-25">[ALP S-044]</HIGHLIGHTER>
											</PARA>
										</RECORD>
										<RECORD id="0-0-0-114085" number="61229" version="713">
											<PARA>(L.L. 2019/218, 12/15/2019, eff. 12/15/2019) <HIGHLIGHTER style="ALP" style-name-escaped="ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-25">[ALP S-044]</HIGHLIGHTER>
											</PARA>
										</RECORD>
									</LEVEL>
								</LEVEL>
								<LEVEL style-name="Section" style-name-escaped="Section" style-id="0-0-0-703" level-depth="9" toc-section="true">
									<RECORD id="0-0-0-114074" number="61230" version="235">
										<HEADING>§ 26-2702 Mitchell-Lama development waiting list report.</HEADING>
										<PARA>
											<DESTINATION id="0-0-0-19421" name="26-2702"/>§ 26-2702 Mitchell-Lama development waiting list report.</PARA>
									</RECORD>
									<LEVEL style-name="Normal Level" style-name-escaped="Normal-Level" style-id="0-0-0-0" level-depth="0" toc-section="false">
										<RECORD id="0-0-0-114084" number="61231" version="235">
											<PARA>By September 1, 2021 and by September 1 of each year thereafter, the department shall submit to the mayor, the speaker of the council and the public advocate, and post to its website, a report on waiting lists for Mitchell-Lama developments that have been digitized and are incorporated into the housing portal required by section 26-1802. Such report shall be disaggregated by each Mitchell-Lama development and include, but need not be limited to, the following: <HIGHLIGHTER style="ALP" style-name-escaped="ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-25">[ALP S-044]</HIGHLIGHTER>
											</PARA>
										</RECORD>
										<RECORD id="0-0-0-114083" number="61232" version="235">
											<PARA>
												<TAB tab-count="1"/>1.<TAB tab-count="1"/>The number of unique applicants on the waiting list on the last day of the prior calendar year; <HIGHLIGHTER style="ALP" style-name-escaped="ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-25">[ALP S-044]</HIGHLIGHTER>
											</PARA>
										</RECORD>
										<RECORD id="0-0-0-114082" number="61233" version="235">
											<PARA>
												<TAB tab-count="1"/>2.<TAB tab-count="1"/>The number of applicants on the waiting list: <HIGHLIGHTER style="ALP" style-name-escaped="ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-25">[ALP S-044]</HIGHLIGHTER>
											</PARA>
										</RECORD>
										<RECORD id="0-0-0-114081" number="61234" version="235">
											<PARA>
												<TAB tab-count="1"/>
												<TAB tab-count="1"/>(a)<TAB tab-count="1"/>Who were not selected for occupancy in such development within the prior calendar year; and <HIGHLIGHTER style="ALP" style-name-escaped="ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-25">[ALP S-044]</HIGHLIGHTER>
											</PARA>
										</RECORD>
										<RECORD id="0-0-0-114080" number="61235" version="235">
											<PARA>
												<TAB tab-count="1"/>
												<TAB tab-count="1"/>(b)<TAB tab-count="1"/>Whose position on the waiting list was sequentially prior to a person other than a veteran who was selected for occupancy in such development within the prior calendar year; <HIGHLIGHTER style="ALP" style-name-escaped="ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-25">[ALP S-044]</HIGHLIGHTER>
											</PARA>
										</RECORD>
										<RECORD id="0-0-0-114079" number="61236" version="235">
											<PARA>
												<TAB tab-count="1"/>3.<TAB tab-count="1"/>The number of substantiated complaints received within the prior calendar year regarding the waiting list for such development, including, but not limited to: <HIGHLIGHTER style="ALP" style-name-escaped="ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-25">[ALP S-044]</HIGHLIGHTER>
											</PARA>
										</RECORD>
										<RECORD id="0-0-0-114078" number="61237" version="235">
											<PARA>
												<TAB tab-count="1"/>
												<TAB tab-count="1"/>(a)<TAB tab-count="1"/>The selection for occupancy of an applicant whose position on the waiting list was sequentially later than applicants who were not selected for occupancy in such development from the same waiting list within the prior calendar year; and <HIGHLIGHTER style="ALP" style-name-escaped="ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-25">[ALP S-044]</HIGHLIGHTER>
											</PARA>
										</RECORD>
										<RECORD id="0-0-0-114077" number="61238" version="235">
											<PARA>
												<TAB tab-count="1"/>
												<TAB tab-count="1"/>(b)<TAB tab-count="1"/>The waiting list process; and <HIGHLIGHTER style="ALP" style-name-escaped="ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-25">[ALP S-044]</HIGHLIGHTER>
											</PARA>
										</RECORD>
										<RECORD id="0-0-0-114076" number="61239" version="235">
											<PARA>
												<TAB tab-count="1"/>4.<TAB tab-count="1"/>The number of applicants who were admitted under the preference for veterans for such development within the prior calendar year. <HIGHLIGHTER style="ALP" style-name-escaped="ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-25">[ALP S-044]</HIGHLIGHTER>
											</PARA>
										</RECORD>
										<RECORD id="0-0-0-114073" number="61240" version="713">
											<PARA>(L.L. 2019/218, 12/15/2019, eff. 12/15/2019) <HIGHLIGHTER style="ALP" style-name-escaped="ALP" name="ALP" id="0-0-0-25">[ALP S-044]</HIGHLIGHTER>
											</PARA>
										</RECORD>
									</LEVEL>
								</LEVEL>
							</LEVEL>
						</LEVEL>
					</LEVEL>
				</LEVEL>
			</LEVEL>
		</LEVEL>
	</LEVEL>
</DOCUMENT>